"This is a good, enjoyable beer, which I find to be true to the style.  I read some of the reviews where people are venting their spleens, and I think it's a bit much.  It is true that the bourbon barrel taste is virtually non- existant, and I understand people get hacked about that because it usually adds about $2 to the price, when declared.  But when I see ratings at the the level of piss in a bottle, it's way overboard.  This is a good, not great or unique Quad."
